- Token bucket algorithm for burst handling
- Per-endpoint customization via route metadata","status":"closed","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-11T10:11:10.906305868-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-12T02:33:26.507874496-05:00","closed_at":"2026-01-12T02:33:26.507874496-05:00","close_reason":"Completed: Implemented rate limit middleware with InMemoryRateLimiter, key generators (byIP, byAPIKey, byUser, byWorkspace), rateLimitMiddleware and strictRateLimitMiddleware for Hono, standard X-RateLimit headers, 429 with Retry-After, preset configurations, and 31 tests"}
